						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa Rajēndra III Year 15, Raudra, Tulā, Purva 13, Monday, Rēvati = 1260, Oct. 18.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records that a horse merchant of Malai-maṇḍalam, called Iravi Mūrtti Nāyakkaṉ made a flower garden with a well at Tripurāntakam in Moḍapaḷḷ-nāḍu of Vēṅgai-maṇḍalam.</p>						

